---
title: Speedy Asian Chicken Tacos with Slaw & Crushed Peanuts
description: Save time at dinner and still end up with a tasty spread of delicous flavours! Tender chicken in a honey-soy glaze gets loaded into these fun tacos, along with a creamy slaw and crunchy nuts. You're in for a family feast!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/speedy-asian-chicken-tacos-2f0a2e10.jpg
